      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>honey</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>Dijon</strong> <strong>mustard </strong>(not a mustard fan? Go easy!),<strong> </strong>the<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and mix until combined – this is your <strong>honey mustard dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1609258653798-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
