            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drizzle with a little of the <strong>honey mustard dressing </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and return the tray[s] to the oven for 5-6 min or until the goats' cheese has started to melt – these are your <strong>goats' cheese & sun-dried tomato toasts</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Ordered extra halloumi? Slice and cook in a pan with a little oil for 4-6 min or until golden all over</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1609258677627-x200.jpg",
