        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the toasts and halved tomatoes are in the oven, peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p><p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>and the <strong>cooked quinoa</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
