          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the goats' cheese & sun-dried tomato toasts are done, remove the tray[s] from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>roasted tomatoes </strong>and <strong>remaining honey mustard dressing</strong> to the bowl with the quinoa and gently toss everything together – this is your <strong>quinoa salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
